snippet.title: A Bewitching Revolution - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
A Bewitching Revolution is an upcoming first-person adventure game about a communist witch living in a cyberpunk city. Use magic to help the city's residents organise collective forms of power and resistance!

Store page: https://colestia.itch.io/a-bewitching-revolution
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/968500/A_Bewitching_Revolution/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/colestia3
Tumblr: https://www.tumblr.com/blog/colestia

Voiceover: justbyou - https://www.fiverr.com/justbyou/record-a-high-quality-female-voice-over-today
Music: Smooth Steering by NY Vice - https://soundcloud.com/vice80s/smooth-steering
